languages.text: "А сегодня ты заработал пятнадцать талонов за вахту потому, что трудишься за троих, верно? Или ты прибил своих дружков в темном углу и отобрал их долю?"
"And today you earned fifteen cards in a single shift because you do the work of three people, right? Or did you take your pals to a dark corner somewhere, do them in, and take their share?"

languages.text: «Y hoy te has ganado quince tarjetas en un solo turno porque has hecho el trabajo de tres, ¿no? ¿O es que te has llevado a tus compañeros a un túnel oscuro, te los has cargado y te has quedado su parte?».

languages.text: 「つまり、今日は3人分の仕事をこなしたから、1回のシフトで15枚稼いだんだな？それとも仲間をどこか暗い隅の方に連れて行って、そいつらをやりこめて、分け前を奪ったのか？」
languages.original_text: "And today you earned fifteen cards in a single shift because you do the work of three people, right? Or did you take your pals to a dark corner somewhere, do them in, and take their share?"

languages.text: “那你今天一天就弄到了十五张配给卡，是因为你做了三个人的工作吗？还是说，你把你的工友带到了某个阴暗的角落里，害死了他们，拿走了他们的配给卡？”
languages.original_text: "And today you earned fifteen cards in a single shift because you do the work of three people, right? Or did you take your pals to a dark corner somewhere, do them in, and take their share?"

languages.text: "Und heute habt Ihr fünfzehn Marken in einer Schicht verdient, weil Ihr die Arbeit von drei Leuten erledigt, richtig? Oder habt Ihr Eure Kameraden in eine dunkle Ecke geführt, Euch ihrer entledigt und ihren Anteil an Euch genommen?"
languages.original_text: "And today you earned fifteen cards in a single shift because you do the work of three people, right? Or did you take your pals to a dark corner somewhere, do them in, and take their share?"

languages.text: « Et tu vas nous faire croire qu'aujourd'hui, t'as gagné quinze tickets d'un coup parce que t'as travaillé comme trois, c'est ça ? Ce serait pas plutôt parce que t'as refroidi deux de tes copains dans un coin sombre pour pouvoir prendre leurs parts ? »
